snippet.title: Shan Smith Reacts To Shocking 'Survivor' S41 Blindside, Reveals Biggest Regret | EXTENDED
snippet.description:
Speaking with ET Canada, Toronto's very own Shan Smith reacts to last week's shocking blindside that led to her torch being snuffed on "Survivor". Tune in to new episodes of "Survivor" season 41 Wednesdays at 8 p.m. ET/PT on Global.
